Cookie-banner filtering
-----------------------
Quell's cookie-banner rules — the curated set (extension/rules/cookie-cmp.json,
the seed selectors in extension/src/content/cookies.js) and the generated set
(extension/rules/cookie-cmp-easylist.json, cookie-generic.css,
cookie-domains.json — regenerated by pipeline/build_rules.py) — derive from the
EasyList Cookie List (published as "Fanboy Cookie Monster").

